articles.title: Insuring your pet? You should know about these changes to Florida law
articles.mainIdea: Insuring your pet? You should know about these changes to Florida law
articles.summary: South Florida Sun Sentinel: Insuring your pet? You should know about these changes to Florida law. As vet bills skyrocket, more and more pet owners are turning to insurance programs to prevent their pets’ surprise illness from becoming a financial hardship. But the devil is in the details, and complaints have surfaced that procedures and care that consumers thought were covered by the policies they purchased actually weren’t covered.
